divs: sighting detailsi was looking on google earth for a new route to get into an area of the desert near my house called adobe town. while folowing a old two track road via google earth i came across what appears to be the outline of a geometric shape and an outline of a human like figure.this figure is about a half mile long from head to foot and can only be seen from the air or google earth. also when viewing the outline of the figure move up nne slightly and you will see a swirl like shape.the area that i discovered this in is extremly remote as you will see in the link i have attached. very few people venture into this area. i am sharing this with you because i don't know who else to share it with. any thoughts you have on this would be greatly appreciated. sincerely (name removed) cms 07\21\2011 19:00 flg note: you will need to download google earth to view the .kmz file if you don't have it already.
